CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 3, 1956, pg. B13 reads: "Celebrating the 21st birthday of the National Achievement Clubs, Inc., were nearly 200 guests Friday at the YWCA. Shown are club dignitaries.  Mrs. Alma Illery, president; Mrs. Goldie Hamilton, financial secretary; Miss Alvenize Barr, first vice president; Miss Myra A. Johns, president emeritus of the board; Mrs. Lillian Williams, Treasurer, and MRs. Mary Clark, first vice president - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of National Achievement Clubs, Inc. officers, from left: Alma Illery, Goldie Hamilton, Alvenize Barr, Myra A. Johns, Lillian Williams, and Mary Clark, gathered behind table for Clubs 21st birthday celebration in YWCA
